{"thag10.2:0.1":"Theragatha 10.2 ","thag10.2:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","thag10.2:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag10.2:0.4":"Ekavihariyattheragatha ","thag10.2:1.1":"“Purato pacchato vapi, ","thag10.2:1.2":"aparo ce na vijjati; ","thag10.2:1.3":"Ativa phasu bhavati, ","thag10.2:1.4":"ekassa vasato vane. ","thag10.2:2.1":"Handa eko gamissami, ","thag10.2:2.2":"arannam buddhavannitam; ","thag10.2:2.3":"Phasu ekaviharissa, ","thag10.2:2.4":"pahitattassa bhikkhuno. ","thag10.2:3.1":"Yogi-pitikaram rammam, ","thag10.2:3.2":"mattakunjarasevitam; ","thag10.2:3.3":"Eko attavasi khippam, ","thag10.2:3.4":"pavisissami kananam. ","thag10.2:4.1":"Supupphite sitavane, ","thag10.2:4.2":"sitale girikandare; ","thag10.2:4.3":"Gattani parisincitva, ","thag10.2:4.4":"cankamissami ekako. ","thag10.2:5.1":"Ekakiyo adutiyo, ","thag10.2:5.2":"ramaniye mahavane; ","thag10.2:5.3":"Kadaham viharissami, ","thag10.2:5.4":"katakicco anasavo. ","thag10.2:6.1":"Evam me kattukamassa, ","thag10.2:6.2":"adhippayo samijjhatu; ","thag10.2:6.3":"Sadhayissamahamyeva, ","thag10.2:6.4":"nanno annassa karako. ","thag10.2:7.1":"Esa bandhami sannaham, ","thag10.2:7.2":"pavisissami kananam; ","thag10.2:7.3":"Na tato nikkhamissami, ","thag10.2:7.4":"appatto asavakkhayam. ","thag10.2:8.1":"Malute upavayante, ","thag10.2:8.2":"site surabhigandhike; ","thag10.2:8.3":"Avijjam dalayissami, ","thag10.2:8.4":"nisinno nagamuddhani. ","thag10.2:9.1":"Vane kusumasanchanne, ","thag10.2:9.2":"pabbhare nuna sitale; ","thag10.2:9.3":"Vimuttisukhena sukhito, ","thag10.2:9.4":"ramissami giribbaje. ","thag10.2:10.1":"Soham paripunnasankappo, ","thag10.2:10.2":"cando pannaraso yatha; ","thag10.2:10.3":"Sabbasavaparikkhino, ","thag10.2:10.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo”ti. ","thag10.2:10.5":"… Ekavihariyo thero …. "}